{"tid":2499694,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓最美變性人河莉秀公開變性前舊照！是長腿清秀美男子啊～","createTime":"2021-04-22T05:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T05:46:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"11aa6d8e64f4c5be3ce6debe8c5da0cd5c75f5b2","tid":2499694,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_5d29f92ff091e42ac62ef09435343e8a/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-22/135021-904000.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_5d29f92ff091e42ac62ef09435343e8a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-22%2F135021-904000.png&h=097f8577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被稱為韓國最美變性藝人的河莉秀公開了變性手術前的照片。<br />\n<br />\n河莉秀是韓國著名的變性藝人，曾一度活躍在韓國和日本的娛樂圈。 1975年出生的河莉秀少年時期因為行為上有些偏女性，常常被人說不男不女。 外界的非議讓河莉秀對自己的性別產生了質疑，當她發現穿上女裝時不會被懷疑性別，她索性就穿上了女裝。 18歲的河莉秀離家出走，到酒吧打工，還交到了男朋友。 為了男友，河莉秀從20歲起便開始接受變性手術。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_23a657af906171a823ed2285c1645543/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-22/135021-903999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_23a657af906171a823ed2285c1645543%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-22%2F135021-903999.jpg&h=2f0da95b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1998年23歲的河莉秀成功完成了變性，之後又被星探看重正式進入娛樂圈，更在2007年和小4歲的圈外男友結婚，在此期間關於他們夫妻的謠言不斷，但兩人始終堅守住了自己的愛情。 只是最終傳出因為河莉秀無法生育、跟丈夫關係變差，兩人於2017年離婚。<br />\n<br />\n變身成為女生已經有20多年了，河莉秀難得公開變性前的男生照片，這次她透露是在整理父親遺物時發現了自己高三時候的男生照。 照片裡的河莉秀身形高挑瘦弱，尤其是一雙大長腿十分吸睛，雖然正臉有些模糊，但能隱約看出秀氣，顏值非常高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_af9cd965af1b2d1a02547bc5590558dd/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-22/135021-904001.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_af9cd965af1b2d1a02547bc5590558dd%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-22%2F135021-904001.png&h=6fe30096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「圖：IG@risu_ha」"},{"pid":"3a712a6850fc0f45c433fb0fab77f8ed5924f855","tid":2499694,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:39:16.000Z","msg":"唔好搞咁多嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912bd2731ecc6c5e014c5bfc1d945493d62e7bf5","tid":2499694,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"你又啱..？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7224633552828263583727e1ce0afc9556017168","tid":2499694,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"男的也好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce812ba15997401b3d491ef8502953f7d7514af","tid":2499694,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:45:04.000Z","msg":"好老下喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0017de5e3b6640d27fb1d1111754a9e091afb7","tid":2499694,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:46:45.000Z","msg":"佢無變性依家會係幾多歲"}]}